summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to certain City-owned property located at the intersection of Ninth Avenue and Lenora Street in the City of Seattle; authorizing the Director of the Fleets and Facilities Department to execute an agreement with the State of Washington Secretary of State to create a nonresidential condominium on the property and to convey certain units therein to the State of Washington in connection with the operation of the Washington Talking Book and Braille Library, and authorizing execution of related agreements.
